# <Random Entertainment>

## URL : https://franklinamanda34.github.io/joke-generator/

## Description

We as a team, Wanted to Create our project to demonstrate our skill using multiple serverside APIS. We also used Purecss as our CSS Framework. The four serverside APIS we used are for entertainment purposes. We used Giphy Developers as one of our APIS to generate random gifs. There is also a random Kanye Quote API that we used to get random quotes. A random joke API is also one of the APIS we used to create a Theme for our project as a Random entertainment website. Lastly a random fact API is our last API.




## Usage

-At the top of the page there is our title and nav links to bring you to desired entertainment. By clicking any of the nav links it will direct you to clicked nav link.

-By clicking the buttons on desired entertainment block you will get any entertainment requested.

-You may search up any gif you want and it will git you that requested gif rated pg-13.

-By searching a gif it will record your search and pu it into local storage to create a search history.

## Technologies used

-HTML

-CSS

-PURECSS
https://purecss.io/

-Javascript

-Giphy Developers
https://developers.giphy.com/

useless facts API
https://uselessfacts.jsph.pl/api/v2/facts/random

-Joke API
https://official-joke-api.appspot.com/random_joke

-Kanye Quote API
https://api.kanye.rest

