## Features

-Giphy Generator

search desired gif or just click get random gif to get gif.

-Kanye Quote Generator

Click Generate button to to get random Kanye quote

-Useless Fact Generator

Click get useless fact to get random fact.

-Random Joke

Click Get A Joke button to get a random Joke.

